#

Maple-Glazed Salmon with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$25.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

SeafoodComfort FoodAmerican Cuisine

Description

A succulent salmon fillet glazed with a sweet and savory maple sauce, served with creamy garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Maple syrup: 3 tablespoons
  • Soy sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Potatoes: 2 large, peeled and cubed
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Cream: 1/4 cup
  • Chives: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
